name: You've Got A Lot Of Guts Coming Here
Lore: 'The Empire, Lando Calrissian, Jabba the Hutt. For Han Solo, it can be very hard to tell when your past is going to catch up with you.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Unique (•) Rebels of ability = 3 are power and forfeit +1 (or power and forfeit +2 if at a Cloud City or Jabba''s Palace site). While Han at a battleground, opponent retrieves no Force from Scum And Villainy. (Immune to Alter.)',
